{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775887576140,"sessionID":"ses_284daec25ffeYvCPebmDHCWqiD","part":{"id":"prt_d7b25ec1f001f50N9sl2uQqp0n","messageID":"msg_d7b25db84001olROpBq4ForLE2","sessionID":"ses_284daec25ffeYvCPebmDHCWqiD","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-fad2aa2d2fca4878ab0e44c43a5a0bbf","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: // Package v1alpha1 contains API Schema definitions for the runtime v1alpha1 API group.\n2: //\n3: // This package provides:\n4: // - Custom resource definitions for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter\n5: // - Shared types for sandbox configuration (containers, volumes, probes, security contexts)\n6: // - Shared constants for default values, runtime types, protocols, and resource limits\n7: // - Validation helper functions for runtime types, protocols, seccomp profiles, timeouts, and ports\n8: //\n9: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n10: // +k8s:conversion-gen=github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis\n11: // +k8s:openapi-gen=true\n12: // +k8s:defaulter-gen=TypeMeta\n13: // +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n14: package v1alpha1\n\n(End of file - total 14 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"// Package v1alpha1 contains API Schema definitions for the runtime v1alpha1 API group.\n//\n// This package provides:\n// - Custom resource definitions for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter\n// - Shared types for sandbox configuration (containers, volumes, probes, security contexts)\n// - Shared constants for default values, runtime types, protocols, and resource limits\n// - Validation helper functions for runtime types, protocols, seccomp profiles, timeouts, and ports\n//\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n// +k8s:conversion-gen=github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis\n// +k8s:openapi-gen=true\n// +k8s:defaulter-gen=TypeMeta\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\npackage v1alpha1","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go","time":{"start":1775887576123,"end":1775887576138}}}}
